 <!--

- any loot can become level 0,1,2 or 3 when opened, the chances would be 20/4/1 (probabilities defined in gamesettings)
- the multipliers would be 1x common, 3x uncommon, 6x rare (multipliers defined in gamesettings)
- common loot would include one item from common, if common group is empty, there's no additional items
- uncommon would include item from both common and uncommon
- rare would include items from common, uncommon, and rare classes

- credit and energy chips would be spawned by value and they would not be defined in the loot tables below separately
- basevalue for enemies would be hitpoints divided by 20 (divisor defined in gamesettings)
- basevalue for lootables would be the defined basevalue
- for example the common premium box below would include 40 energy or credit chips plus the item loot of credit box or medikit
- credit chips are multiplied by the loot multiplier

- basevalue is basically the number of credits spawned from the box multiplied by the energy/credits ratio (with 0.5 ratio, 40 basevalue will yield 20 credits at 1.0 loot multiplier)

 -->

